Package: hespdiv
Type: Package
Title: Recursive, hierarchical spatial data partitioning based on manually defined criterias 
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2023-11-06
Author: Liudas  Daumantas <liudas.daumantas@chgf.vu.lt>
Maintainer: Liudas  Daumantas <liudas.daumantas@chgf.vu.lt>
Description: Provides functions for hierarchical data subdivision in space. The main
function hespdiv produces topologically contiguous clusters in geographical space
based on manually defined or preset subdivision methods.
Other function allow further analysis of the results, various visualisation options,
as well as means to perform sensitivity analysis. Note that blok3D may only work
properly on windows OS.
